"5. Certificate Authorities" : "5. ì¸ì¦ ê¸°ê´€"
"Certificate Authorities" : "ì¸ì¦ ê¸°ê´€"
"A certificate authority (CA) is a third-party organization with 3 main objectives:" : "ì¸ì¦ ê¸°ê´€(CA)ì€ 3ê°€ì§€ ì£¼ìš” ëª©í‘œë¥¼ ê°€ì§„ íƒ€ì‚¬ ì¡°ì§ì´ì•¼."
"1. Issuing certificates." : "1. ì¸ì¦ì„œ ë°œê¸‰."
"2. Confirming the identity of the certificate owner." : "2. ì¸ì¦ì„œ ì†Œìœ ìì˜ ì‹ ì› í™•ì¸."
"3. Providing proof that the certificate is valid." : "3. ì¸ì¦ì„œê°€ ìœ íš¨í•˜ë‹¤ëŠ” ì¦ê±° ì œê³µ."
"You might have heard of Symantec, Comodo, or Let's Encrypt, among others." : "ë„ˆëŠ” ì•„ë§ˆ Symantec, Comodo, or Let's Encryptë¥¼ ë“¤ì–´ë³¸ì ì´ ìˆì„êº¼ì•¼."
